com.quantcomponents.algo
Interface ITradingAgentHierarchyContainer

All Known Implementing Classes:
MemoryTradingAgentHierarchyContainer
public interface ITradingAgentHierarchyContainer

Container for trading algorithm hierarchy. Used internally to decouple the ITradingManager from the storage of the algo trading hierarchy Implementations can use database or other means of providing persistence

See Also:
ITradingManager
